{"title":"递归数列","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1836","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个由自然数组成的数列按下式定义：</p>\n<p>对于i &lt;= k：ai = bi </p>\n<p>对于i &gt; k: ai = c1ai-1 + c2ai-2 + ... + ckai-k</p>\n<p>其中bj 和 cj （1&lt;=j&lt;=k）是给定的自然数。写一个程序，给定自然数m &lt;= n, <span style=\"\">计算</span>am + am+1 + am+2 + ... + an, <span style=\"\">并输出它除以给定自然数</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">p</span><span style=\"\">的余数的值。</span> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行是一个自然数k。</p>\n<p>第二行包含k个自然数b1, b2,...,bk。</p>\n<p>第三行包含k个自然数c1, c2,...,ck。</p>\n<p>第四行包含三个自然数m, n, p。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p class=\"p0\">输出文件spp.out仅包含一行：一个正整数，表示(am&nbsp;+&nbsp;am+1&nbsp;+&nbsp;am+2&nbsp;+&nbsp;...&nbsp;+&nbsp;an)&nbsp;mod&nbsp;p的值。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2</p>\n<p>1 1</p>\n<p>1 1</p>\n<p>2 10 1000003</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>142</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<div>\n<p>对于<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">100%</span><span style=\"\">的测试数据：</span></p>\n<p>1&lt;= k &lt;=15</p>\n<p>1 &lt;= m &lt;= n &lt;= 10<sup>18</sup></p>\n<p>对于<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">20%</span><span style=\"\">的测试数据：</span></p>\n<p>1&lt;= k &lt;=15</p>\n<p>1 &lt;= m &lt;= n &lt;= 10<sup>6</sup></p>\n<p>对于<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">30%</span><span style=\"\">的测试数据：</span></p>\n<p>k=1</p>\n<p>1 &lt;= m &lt;= n &lt;= 10<sup>18</sup></p>\n<p>对于所有测试数据：<br>0&lt;= b1, b2,... bk, c1, c2,..., ck&lt;=10<sup>9</sup></p>\n<p>1 &lt;= p &lt;= 10<sup>8</sup></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}